<Layout title="About">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <h2><span style="view-transition-name: title;">About</span></h2>
    <section>
      <p>
        I (<a
          href="https://x.com/taroj1205"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">taroj1205</a
        >) am a developer based in New Zealand, and a student at University of
        Auckland.
      </p>
      <p>
        I was born in 2005 in Tokyo, and I moved to Ehime after the 2011
        earthquake.
      </p>
      <p>
        I went to New Zealand for the first time in 2017, and went to the local
        junior high school in Auckland for a year.
      </p>
      <p>
        I went to Cebu, Philippines for three months in 2018 to study English,
        then I went to a local junior high school in Cebu for a year.
      </p>
      <p>
        I went back to New Zealand for the second time in 2019, and went to the
        local junior high school in Auckland for five years.
      </p>
      <p>
        I had an ACL injury in 2019 from playing football. I was told I'm too
        young for surgery, so I started physio for rehabilitation.
      </p>
      <p>
        After a year of rehabilitation, I returned to light sports and tore my
        ACL a second time in 2020. I had surgery and recovered from the injury.
        I started playing various sports like football, table tennis, and
        badminton.
      </p>
      <p>
        At the end of 2024, I tore my ACL for the third time while playing
        football. I started going to the gym to train and get back into sports.
      </p>
